Release
LTS.418.4
of July 9, 2024
New features
1. The
Condition Tree updated: new field types were added; conditions/nodes can now be moved via drag & drop throughout all levels; Tree can be called in algorithms using the
objectsWithOptions
function.
2. The
Login page constructor
settings can now be applied to the mobile application.
3.
The
Table dashboard
has new option to choose the visual which opens after clicking the hyperlink.
Changes and improvements
Value validation check is now occurring during
self-registration
by e-mail;
Analytical panels settings were improved, now height is set in % of user’s screen size and width is set in % of container size;
Display of OLAP tables imported in Excel was improved;
Display of versioning dates in Communication panel was improved, panel’s size was adjusted for small screens;
"Title by attribute" widget
was improved;
Added limitations to edit instances’ data for users with “Read” permissions in “Object registry” widget;
Filtering of values added for related objects in “Type attribute” field;
Multiple choice option in default attributes was stabilized;
Execution of transitions in business processes were improved, now newly created versions work according to their original versions;
Now non-administrator users are unable to block their own personal account;
Display of images sent in email using print form template was stabilized;
Transfer of permission settings when installing update packages was improved;
Placement of custom buttons in Control panel was optimized;
Dashboards opening time was improved;
Edoc improvements: print form generation by algorithm and value filtering in object parameters were optimized;
Visual and registry of
Expressions/Autocalculations
object type instances was improved.
"Object chat" widget
was improved;
Sending system notification when setting up deadlines in several stages at once. of an overdue task was stabilized;
Launching application via /hook was stabilized.
